# 620014

LYMPHATIC MALFORMATION 12; LMPHM12


INHERITANCE
- Autosomal recessive [SNOMEDCT: 258211005 ] [UMLS: C0441748 HPO: HP:0000007 ] [HPO: HP:0000007 ]

HEAD & NECK
Eyes
- Edema around eyes [SNOMEDCT: 49563000 ] [UMLS: C0151205 HPO: HP:0100539 ]
- Edema of eyelids [SNOMEDCT: 89091004 ] [ICD10CM: H02.84 ] [ICD9CM: 374.82 ] [UMLS: C0162285 HPO: HP:0100540 ]
- Ptosis [SNOMEDCT: 29696001 , 11934000 ] [ICD10CM: H02.409 , H02.40 , H02.4 ] [ICD9CM: 374.30 , 374.3 ] [UMLS: C0005745 , C0033377 HPO: HP:0000508 ] [HPO: HP:0000508 ]

CARDIOVASCULAR
Heart
- Pericardial effusion [SNOMEDCT: 373945007 ] [UMLS: C0031039 , C1253937 HPO: HP:0001698 ] [HPO: HP:0001698 ]
- Mitral valve prolapse [SNOMEDCT: 409712001 , 8074002 ] [UMLS: C0026267 HPO: HP:0001634 ] [HPO: HP:0001634 ]
- Ventricular septal defect [SNOMEDCT: 253549006 , 30288003 , 768552007 ] [ICD10CM: Q21.0 ] [ICD9CM: 745.4 ] [UMLS: C0018818 HPO: HP:0001629 ] [HPO: HP:0001629 ]
Vascular
- Patent foramen ovale [SNOMEDCT: 204317008 , 204315000 ] [ICD10CM: Q21.12 , Q21.11 ] [ICD9CM: 745.5 ] [UMLS: C0016522 , C0344724 HPO: HP:0001655 , HP:0001684 ] [HPO: HP:0001655 ]

RESPIRATORY
Lung
- Pleural effusions, recurrent chylous [UMLS: C5775561 ] [SNOMEDCT: 60046008 ] [ICD10CM: J90 ] [ICD9CM: 511.9 ]
- Pulmonary hypoplasia [SNOMEDCT: 80825009 ] [UMLS: C0265783 HPO: HP:0002089 ] [HPO: HP:0002089 ]
- Frequent infections [SNOMEDCT: 451991000124106 ] [UMLS: C0239998 HPO: HP:0002719 ] [HPO: HP:0002719 ]

CHEST
- Chylothorax [SNOMEDCT: 83035003 ] [UMLS: C0008733 HPO: HP:0010310 ] [HPO: HP:0010310 ]
- Dilated thoracic duct [UMLS: C5775556 ]
- Hypoplastic or absent thoracic duct [UMLS: C5775557 ]
Ribs Sternum Clavicles & Scapulae
- Pectus excavatum [SNOMEDCT: 391982004 , 391987005 ] [ICD10CM: Q67.6 ] [ICD9CM: 754.81 ] [UMLS: C0016842 , C2051831 HPO: HP:0000767 ] [HPO: HP:0000767 ]

ABDOMEN
- Ascites [SNOMEDCT: 389026000 ] [ICD10CM: R18 , R18.8 ] [ICD9CM: 789.5 ] [UMLS: C0003962 HPO: HP:0001541 ] [HPO: HP:0001541 ]
- Retrograde mesenteric lymph flow [UMLS: C5775558 ]

GENITOURINARY
External Genitalia (Male)
- Hydrocele [SNOMEDCT: 386152007 , 26614003 ] [ICD10CM: N43.3 ] [ICD9CM: 603 , 603.9 ] [UMLS: C1720771 HPO: HP:0000034 , HP:0100673 ] [HPO: HP:0000034 ]

SKIN, NAILS, & HAIR
Skin
- Subcutaneous edema [UMLS: C3670763 ]
- Large cutaneous lymph channels [UMLS: C5775559 ]
- Lymphedema below the knees [UMLS: C5775560 ]

PRENATAL MANIFESTATIONS
- Hydrops fetalis, nonimmune [SNOMEDCT: 276509008 , 206538000 ] [ICD9CM: 778.0 ] [UMLS: C0455988 HPO: HP:0001790 ] [HPO: HP:0001790 ]
Amniotic Fluid
- Polyhydramnios [SNOMEDCT: 86203003 ] [ICD10CM: O40 ] [ICD9CM: 657.0 , 657 ] [UMLS: C0020224 HPO: HP:0001561 ] [HPO: HP:0001561 ]
Placenta & Umbilical Cord
- Edematous placenta [SNOMEDCT: 56425003 ] [UMLS: C0566703 ]

MISCELLANEOUS
- Variable severity [UMLS: C1861403 HPO: HP:0003828 ] [HPO: HP:0003828 ]
- Variable features may be present
- Affected individuals may be stillborn due to hydrops fetalis

MOLECULAR BASIS
- Caused by mutation in the MYOD family inhibitor domain-containing protein gene (MDFIC, 614511.0001 )
